Author: TwilightPunkster K64#7533
Content:
So, the update of today. If you didn't knew, RedFOX Labs is accelerating projects in South East Asia, but but but, I had an awesome talk with @Bitcoin Benny. More news to come, so cooking up stuff in the kitchen. Meanwhile in the batcave, I have started to working on a long term plan for the gaming SDK's, and together with @FishyGuts thinking about a profile for us to set out. Thanks to @Mylo we got 90 days to bring our best out to apply for grants, and @Meyse keeps feeding me game ideas. Tomorrow, I've a meeting with a potential 2d artist, tuesday getting budgets, marketing and branding alive with cool stuff. Komodore64 has a way more retro look and the skillful fingers and help from our hero @Steve Lee are praised with hands reaching the roof. It's sunday, and we are cooking, planning, moving, hyping and fired up.

Together we are strong.

Author: TwilightPunkster K64#7533
Content: Today's grand news - just kidding. Offices tuned, gamified and a boilerplate of 270Gb of game assets pure for fun and profit, and wrapping up the last parts of it. Pretty much, we can now build almost *anything*. Hardware set up, and we have a rough plan of things; hopefully our team gets an extra power up, so fingers crossed. I made a small plan for world domination and bought some donuts. Keeping ya'll posted!
